milestones.description: Wasim Raja and Azeem Hafeez's 31-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 28 between Abdul Qadir and Rashid Khan
Wasim Raja has broken the record for most catches (24) in ODIs for PAK, going past Javed Miandad's 23
Gavaskar has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (60) for IND, going past Kapil Dev
